OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779984666
OL,3,CTeenager who died in bank holiday lake
OL,4,Ctragedy named
OL,6,FIt added: "His loss has deeply
OL,7,Faffected everyone who knew him, and
OL,8,Fthe pain felt by his family and loved
OL,9,Fones is unimaginable.
OL,11,F"During this incredibly difficult
OL,12,Ftime, we want to come together to
OL,13,Fsupport his family and help ease some
OL,14,Fof the financial burden they are
OL,15,Ffacing."
OL,17,FA second fundraiser set up by friend
OL,18,FKelly Osayi said: "He was loved by
OL,19,Fmany people and it is tragic that he
OL,20,Fdied at just the age of 16 which still
OL,21,Fdoesn't feel real for most of us."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
