PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779984666
OL,3,CTeenager who died in bank holiday lake
OL,4,Ctragedy named
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Fpark at 6.50pm on Bank Holiday Monday
OL,8,Fto reports a the boy had entered the
OL,9,Fwater but had failed to emerge.
OL,11,FPolice, South Yorkshire Fire and
OL,12,FRescue Service and the Yorkshire
OL,13,FAmbulance Service were involved in the
OL,14,Fsearch.
OL,16,FMuhammed was one of eight children and
OL,17,Ftwo adults to lose their lives in open
OL,18,Fwater incidents across the country
OL,19,Fover the weekend.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
