PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779984666
OL,3,CTeenager who died in bank holiday lake
OL,4,Ctragedy named
OL,6,FAndrew Bramidge, executive director of
OL,7,Fenvironment at Rotherham Borough
OL,8,FCouncil, which manages Rother Valley
OL,9,FCountry Park, said safety measures
OL,10,Fwere in place before Muhammed's death.
OL,12,FHe added: "We recently increased the
OL,13,Fnumber of regular security patrols and
OL,14,Fstaffing for park maintenance.
OL,16,F"We have staff actively encouraging
OL,17,Fvisitors to stay out of the water, and
OL,18,Fa boat monitoring authorised water
OL,19,Fsports activity on the lake to ensure
OL,20,Fparticipants are safe.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779984666
OL,3,CTeenager who died in bank holiday lake
OL,4,Ctragedy named
OL,6,F"Clear signage is in place to
OL,7,Fdiscourage swimming due to the known
OL,8,Frisks. We also have additional staff
OL,9,Fon site this week to provide support
OL,10,Fand reassurance to visitors."
OL,12,FHe added: "However, we continually
OL,13,Freview safety arrangements, and we
OL,14,Fwill be speaking with partners and
OL,15,Flocal representatives about whether
OL,16,Fany further measures can be put in
OL,17,Fplace as we go into the summer months.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
