OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1779984666
OL,3,CTeenager who died in bank holiday lake
OL,4,Ctragedy named
OL,6,F"Tragic incidents in open water have
OL,7,Fsadly been seen in other parts of the
OL,8,Fcountry in recent days, highlighting
OL,9,Fthe risks that open water can present,
OL,10,Fparticularly in such hot weather.
OL,12,F"We would again urge everyone visiting
OL,13,FRother Valley and our other country
OL,14,Fparks: outside of organised events,
OL,15,Fswimming is not permitted."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
